            <button style="padding: 8px 14px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px; cursor: pointer; margin: 0 8px;" onclick="window.location.href='index.html'">ГўвҖ Вҗ Ana Sayfa</button>
